@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<section class="custom-page-about-section">
    <div class="custom-page-content">
        <div class="about-container">
            <div class="about-header">
                <h1>About Us</h1>
                <p>Welcome to <strong>OUR RECRUITMENT AND JOB SEARCH WEBSITE</strong> — a platform that connects job seekers and employers, aiming to create a convenient, efficient, and seamless space for exploring career opportunities.</p>
            </div>

            <section class="about-section">
                <h2>Vision</h2>
                <p>We strive to become the leading recruitment platform, not only assisting job seekers in finding suitable opportunities but also supporting businesses in sourcing high-quality talent. We are committed to creating an effective job community where both employees and employers can easily connect and grow together.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="about-section">
                <h2>Mission</h2>
                <p>Our goal is to establish a transparent, straightforward, and efficient recruitment ecosystem, thereby contributing to economic development and creating career opportunities for everyone. We are not just a job search website but a bridge to help you find and develop your career while assisting businesses in discovering the right talent for their needs.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="about-section">
                <h2>Commitments</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Simple and user-friendly:</strong> An intuitive interface that is easy to use for everyone.</li>
                    <li><strong>High security:</strong> We are committed to protecting your personal information, ensuring a safe online environment.</li>
                    <li><strong>Constant updates and improvements:</strong> Continuous efforts to enhance technology and services to ensure the platform operates efficiently and reliably.</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <div class="about-footer">
                <p>We are always ready to accompany you on your journey to finding your dream job or the perfect candidate. Start today and let’s build your career future together!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="custom-page-map-container">
        <h2>Our Location</h2>
